23
00:01:15,333 --> 00:01:17,166
Fatherly wisdom!

24
00:01:17,250 --> 00:01:18,958
You'll understand when
you're older, son.

25
00:01:19,041 --> 00:01:20,333
[LEÓN]
You jackass!

