Be gentle.

134
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:43,041
Come. Let me lead.

135
00:07:43,125 --> 00:07:43,708
[BIGAS grunts]

136
00:07:43,791 --> 00:07:44,541
[gasps]

137
00:07:44,625 --> 00:07:46,083
[IRENE gasps]

138
00:07:46,166 --> 00:07:48,750
Somebody tell me why the
hell he's naked in here!

139
00:07:48,833 --> 00:07:50,375
Quick! Irene!

140
00:07:50,458 --> 00:07:52,666
We have... to get out
of here right away.

141
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:54,958
