that whole virgin maiden act?

146
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:06,750
[GERMÁN]
Yeah.

147
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:08,666
Well, Donato, when you're
right, you are right.

148
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:12,583
Eh. Anyone with eyes can see
the man's desperate for it.

149
00:08:12,666 --> 00:08:14,583
[GERMÁN] It seems that
I have been beaten.

150
00:08:14,666 --> 00:08:16,166
