Let's cut him to shreds!

162
00:08:42,833 --> 00:08:44,041
Put 'em up, lover boy!

163
00:08:44,125 --> 00:08:45,750
[CAPI, BIGAS growl]

164
00:08:48,083 --> 00:08:49,041
