166
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,000
[IRENE gasps]

167
00:08:53,083 --> 00:08:54,583
[GERMÁN grunts]

168
00:08:54,666 --> 00:08:55,875
[DONATO grunts]

169
00:08:55,958 --> 00:08:57,583
Aw...! New plan!

170
00:08:57,666 --> 00:09:00,291
[gasping]

171
00:09:00,375 --> 00:09:01,833
